  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if Geranium oil will relieve a variety of
      neuropathic pain and some pain relief will last more than 48 hours.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      EPT 100 study is designed to identify the percentage of people who experience neuropathic
      pain relief from topical geranium oil from Reunion Island, determine which neuropathic pain
      conditions respond best and define the time course of the pain relief.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
